pre.code:
library IncreasedRiskExclusions version '1.0.0'
using FHIR version '4.0.1' include FHIRHelpers version '4.0.1' called FHIRHelpers
include IncreasedRiskExclusionsEvents version '1.0.0' called Events include IncreasedRiskExclusionsActions version '1.0.0' called Actions include DataElements version '1.0.0' called DataElements
context Patient
//------------------------------------------------------------------------------ // RECOMMENDATIONS //------------------------------------------------------------------------------
define "flow-IncreasedRiskExclusions": if Events."eve-HereditarySyndrome" is true then Actions."act-CRCHereditarySyndrome" as Tuple{code Code, reason Code} else if Events."eve-IBD" is true then Actions."act-IBD" as Tuple{code Code, reason Code} else if Events."eve-HxCRC" is true then Actions."act-HxCRC" as Tuple{code Code, reason Code} else if Events."eve-FamilyHx" is true then Actions."act-FamilyHxCRC" as Tuple{code Code, reason Code} else if Events."eve-HxPolyps" is true then Actions."act-HxPolyps" as Tuple{code Code, reason Code} else Actions."act-AvgRiskScreeningEligible" as Tuple{code Code, reason Code}
define IsHereditaryIncRisk: Events."eve-HereditarySyndrome" is true
define IsIBDIncRisk: Events."eve-IBD" is true
define IsHxCRCIncRisk: Events."eve-HxCRC" is true
define IsFamilyHxIncRisk: Events."eve-FamilyHx" is true
define IsHxPolypsIncRisk: Events."eve-HxPolyps" is true
define IsAvgRisk: Events."eve-HereditarySyndrome" is false and Events."eve-IBD" is false and Events."eve-HxCRC" is false and Events."eve-FamilyHx" is false and Events."eve-HxPolyps" is false
